  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.5.1\" data-text=\"Version 1.5.1\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.5.1</h3>\n<p>July 24, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.transition:transition:1.5.1</code> and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.transition:transition-ktx:1.5.1</code> are released. Version 1.5.1 contains <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/997511f658e698f2cc9bfbb485bacdefc476ba19..2d628af7c0127584d10f86a6e0872691a5de4536/transition\">these commits</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed an issue where calls to <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">animateToStart()</code> or <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">animateToEnd()</code> on a seekable transition would be ignored if the transition was not started. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I44d9618604c29659e1f6ae7e966cd1533369b18c\">I44d96</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/338624457\">b/338624457</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
